title: [Dancing Devil Reef, Shipwreck]
description: Battered wooden walls rise from a wide-plank oak floor heavily stained with salt.  Just above a skeletal siren lizard attached to the wall by a long rusty chain hangs a wrought-iron key ring, and an exposed oak rafter ceiling completes the picture.  A iron-banded treasure chest with a smashed lock and a bulging sack obscured under a loose plank stand side by side in the middle of the room.
